public String[][] getNarrowerTerms(String server_url,
                                   String repository,
                                   String username,
                                   String password,
                                   String term,
                                   String TOP_CONCEPT,
                                   String PREDICATE,
                                   String skosVersion,
                                   String virtuosoNamedGraph)
                            throws RemoteException
Find narrower Concepts and their prefLabel.

Parameters:
server_url - the URL of the meta-data server that will be queried (e.g. http://www.host.org:8080/sesame)
repository - the name of the repository or model in the meta-data server (e.g. mem-rdfs-db)
username - the username of the user to access the repository as used by the meta-data server (e.g. testuser)
password - the password of the user to access the repository as used by the meta-data server (e.g. opensesame)
term - the URI of the "broader" skos:Concept, the "focus" concept.
Returns:
an array of pairs of skos:Concepts and their skos:prefLabel
Throws:
RemoteException
